theorem strong_mono_of_strong_mono [StrongMono («expr ≫ » f g)] : StrongMono f :=

      intros
      constructor
      intro u v sq

      exact comm_sq.has_lift.mk' ⟨(comm_sq.mk h₀).lift, by simp, by simp [← cancel_epi z, sq.w]⟩ }
